      • pushParsedRequestPathAndReset

        void pushParsedRequestPathAndReset(ParsedRequest requestPath)
        Set the request path and reset the response. Currently this:
        • sets the ParsedRequest
        • clears the process state map
        • clears the process chain
        • resets the response headers and buffer.
        • clears the used element IDs.
        Parameters:
        requestPath - the request path.

      • setTimeZone

        void setTimeZone(TimeZone tz,
                 @Nullable
                 Boolean saveInSession)
        Set the timeZone.
        Parameters:
        tz - the timeZone. Should not be null. If null, set to UTC or the site default.
        saveInSession - boolean flag that indicates whether or not the timezone should be saved in the session. If null, the timezone will be saved if a session exists; otherwise it won't.
